'''Xabar''' was a [[Species/Legends|species]] of violet-[[Color/Legends|colored]] [[Fungus/Legends|fungus]] that was native to the [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Xagobah/Legends|Xagobah]]. It possessed tentacles that released [[Poison/Legends|toxins]] on contact with foreign objects or other creatures, causing total, but temporary, muscle paralysis. Street youths that were intrigued with the afterlife were known to use it as a drug because of its rigor mortis-like effects.

